uk.ac.nottingham.controllers

Class NotificationDemoController

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.nottingham.controllers.NotificationDemoController

  • public class NotificationDemoController
extends java.lang.Object
    FXML controller for the NotificationDemo.fxml file. It has several functions that are executed on a button press. Allows user to go back to welcome screen or test the notification system on the accompanying android app.
